## 快速启动脚本

### Windows (run.bat)

```batch
@echo off
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py
```

### macOS/Linux (run.sh)

```bash
#!/bin/bash
cd backend
pip install -r requirements.txt
python main.py
```
